      <div data-reveal style="background:#EDE5D4; border-radius:18px; padding:clamp(32px,4vw,48px);">
        <p class="eyebrow">Volunteer</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,34px); line-height:1.12;">Volunteer at the event</h2>
        <p style="margin:18px 0 0; font-size:16.5px; line-height:1.7; color:#4A4A42;">Twelve volunteers will help with class transitions, wayfinding, and participant support throughout the day. Volunteers receive free admission to The Wild Animal Sanctuary.</p>
