      </div>
      <div data-reveal style="border-top:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">When is the event?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">The exact date is still being confirmed. The event is planned for a Saturday or Sunday between mid-August and mid-October 2026.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">What does registration include?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">One 60-minute yoga class and a full-day Sanctuary pass — including the elevated walkway, Welcome Center, and Education Center.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">Can I take more than one class?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">Possibly — a second class may be offered for an additional fee. This is still to be determined and will be confirmed before registration opens.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">Are children allowed?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">The yoga event is open to adults and youth ages 14+ with parental permission. Younger children and family members may purchase Sanctuary admission separately through the Sanctuary ticket office.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">Do I need to bring a yoga mat?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">Yes — please bring your own yoga mat. You may also bring your own food and drink or purchase food and beverages onsite.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">Is there a refund policy?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">No refunds are planned if participants choose to cancel.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">Do I need to sign a waiver?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">Yes. Participants will sign a liability waiver that also includes media consent and an option to share contact information with The Wild Animal Sanctuary.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(43,58,45,0.16);">
          <summary style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:20px; padding:22px 4px; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:20px; color:#2B3A2D;">Is this a guided tour?<span style="color:#B58A47; font-size:24px; font-weight:300;">+</span></summary>
          <p style="margin:0 4px 22px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#5A5A50;">No. Time at the Sanctuary is self-guided, with Sanctuary volunteers available throughout the public areas to answer questions. The event is intentionally simple — no vendor booths, silent auction, or sponsor fair.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

